    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Sphinxcontrib-jsmath Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Sphinxcontrib-jsmath</application> package is a
<application>Sphinx</application> extension which renders display math in
HTML via JavaScript.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

