    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalao de Sphinxcontrib-jsmath</title>

    <para> Build the module: </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user sphinxcontrib-jsmath</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      The installation can be tested with the following commands:
    </para>

<screen remap="test"><userinput>sed -i 's/text()/read_&amp;/' tests/test_jsmath.py &amp;&amp;
pytest</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      the <command>sed ...</command> command is needed because of a change in
<application>Sphinx</application> API for versions greater than 5.0.
    </para>

    </sect3>

